      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey prof, i'm stuck on this syntax tree thing. for the sentence \"the student studied with the book\", my parser is attaching the PP \"with the book\" to the VP (the verb) instead of the NP (the noun). can you explain why the attachment might be going to the verb phrase instead of the noun? thanks",
